---

<section class="py-20 bg-gray-100">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Kemampuan & Keahlian</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Terus berkembang dan mengasah keterampilan untuk menciptakan website yang modern, responsif, dan efektif.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center">
          <i class="fas fa-laptop-code text-white text-6xl"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Website Personal</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Portofolio dan CV online dengan desain modern dan mobile-friendly
          </p>
          <span class="inline-block bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Personal</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center">
          <i class="fas fa-store text-white text-6xl"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Toko Online Sederhana</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Katalog produk dengan integrasi WhatsApp untuk pemesanan cepat
          </p>
          <span class="inline-block bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">E-Commerce</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-500 flex items-center justify-center">
          <i class="fas fa-building text-white text-6xl"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Company Profile</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Website profil bisnis dengan informasi layanan dan kontak yang jelas
          </p>
          <span class="inline-block bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Corporate</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-red-500 flex items-center justify-center">
          <i class="fas fa-bullhorn text-white text-6xl"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Landing Page</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Halaman promosi khusus untuk produk, layanan, atau event
          </p>
          <span class="inline-block bg-orange-100 text-orange-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Landing Page</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-green-500 flex items-center justify-center">
          <i class="fas fa-blog text-white text-6xl"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Blog</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Platform untuk berbagi artikel, opini, dan informasi dengan tampilan menarik
          </p>
          <span class="inline-block bg-teal-100 text-teal-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Blog</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center">
