        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Responsive Design</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Tampilan optimal di semua perangkat, dari desktop hingga smartphone
          </p>
          <span class="inline-block bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Mobile First</span>
        </div>
      </div>
